OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778115794
OL,3,CTrump pauses operation to open Strait
OL,4,Cof Hormuz and pushes for Iran deal
OL,6,FDonald Trump said he has paused
OL,7,Fefforts to guide stranded commercial
OL,8,Fvessels from the Strait of Hormuz in
OL,9,Forder to finalise a deal with Iran to
OL,10,Fend the war.
OL,12,FThe US president made the announcement
OL,13,Fon his Truth Social platform on
OL,14,FTuesday evening and did not
OL,15,Fimmediately respond to requests for
OL,16,Ffurther details.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
