OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778115794
OL,3,CTrump pauses operation to open Strait
OL,4,Cof Hormuz and pushes for Iran deal
OL,6,FHe said the so-called "Project
OL,7,FFreedom" would be "paused for a short
OL,8,Fperiod of time to see whether or not
OL,9,Fthe agreement can be finalised and
OL,10,Fsigned" following a "mutual agreement"
OL,11,Fbetween Pakistan and other countries.
OL,13,FA US blockade of Iranian ports will
OL,14,Fremain in place, and it appears that
OL,15,FIran's own blockade of the Strait of
OL,16,FHormuz will also continue.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
