OL,3,CTrump pauses operation to open Strait
OL,4,Cof Hormuz and pushes for Iran deal
OL,6,FIt comes after tensions hit a critical
OL,7,Fhigh on Sunday and Monday, as the US
OL,8,Fpushed to open up the strait to
OL,9,Fcommercial ships, with conflicting
OL,10,Freports between Washington and Tehran
OL,11,Fover naval skirmishes.
OL,13,FThe US denied a report by Iranian
OL,14,Fmedia that one of its warships was hit
OL,15,Fby Iranian missiles as it tried to
OL,16,Fenter the Strait of Hormuz, while
OL,17,FTehran denied reports that six of its
OL,18,Fvessels had been sunk by the US
OL,19,Fmilitary.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778115794
OL,3,CTrump pauses operation to open Strait
OL,4,Cof Hormuz and pushes for Iran deal
OL,6,FMeanwhile world leaders condemned an
OL,7,FIranian attack on oil infrastructure
OL,8,Fin the UAE on Monday ` the first such
OL,9,Fattack since a ceasefire had been
OL,10,Freached in early April ` pushing the
OL,11,Falready fragile truce into further
OL,12,Fjeopardy.
OL,14,FWashington appears to have taken a
OL,15,Fstep back, however, with Secretary of
OL,16,FState Marco Rubio saying on Tuesday
OL,17,Fthat major US military operations
OL,18,Fagainst Iran are over.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
