PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778115794
OL,3,CTrump pauses operation to open Strait
OL,4,Cof Hormuz and pushes for Iran deal
OL,6,FIt is unclear exactly how the Tehran
OL,7,Fgovernment will respond, but in a post
OL,8,Fon X, the country's semi-official
OL,9,FTasnim News Agency characterised
OL,10,FWashington's "shift in rhetoric" as a
OL,11,Ffailure.
OL,13,F"As Tehran rejects any return of
OL,14,FStrait of Hormuz to pre-war conditions
OL,15,Fwithout justice, the world watches a
OL,16,Fdefeated US administration scramble to
OL,17,Fundo the damage it caused ` while
OL,18,Foffering no answers for the Iranian
OL,19,Fpeople it has harmed."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
