OL,3,CTrump pauses operation to open Strait
OL,4,Cof Hormuz and pushes for Iran deal
OL,6,FSpeaking to reporters Rubio said Iran
OL,7,Fmust agree to US demands on its
OL,8,Fnuclear program and reopen the strait.
OL,9,FIran insists that its uranium
OL,10,Fenrichment programme is only for
OL,11,Fcivilian energy purposes.
OL,13,FBut Rubio said Iranian claims of not
OL,14,Fwanting to develop nuclear weapons are
OL,15,Fnot reflected by its actions, pointing
OL,16,Fto its development of advanced
OL,17,Fcentrifuge technology and construction
OL,18,Fof underground bunkers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
