OL,3,CTrump pauses operation to open Strait
OL,4,Cof Hormuz and pushes for Iran deal
OL,6,FRubio insisted the US operation in the
OL,7,FStrait of Hormuz is defensive only
OL,8,Fdespite recent clashes with Iran.
OL,10,F"There's no shooting unless we're shot
OL,11,Fat first, OK? We're not attacking
OL,12,Fthem. We're not," Rubio told
OL,13,Freporters. "If they pose a threat to
OL,14,Four forces, we'll shoot down drones,
OL,15,Fwe'll shoot down missiles. But it's
OL,16,Fdefensive in nature."
OL,26,@rD@AOUtD@QO]uD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
