OL,3,CTrump pauses operation to open Strait
OL,4,Cof Hormuz and pushes for Iran deal
OL,6,FThe secretary of state said about
OL,7,F23,000 civilian sailors are stranded
OL,8,Fin the Persian Gulf and "left for
OL,9,Fdead" due to Iran's chokehold on the
OL,10,Fstrait.
OL,12,F"They're sitting ducks, they're
OL,13,Fisolated, they're starving, they're
OL,14,Fvulnerable," Rubio said. "At least 10
OL,15,Fsailors have already died as a result."
OL,17,FHe the sailors come from 87 countries
OL,18,Fand are innocent bystanders, adding:
OL,19,F"It's criminal for sure, but it's
OL,20,Fdesperate and destructive to block the
OL,21,FStrait of Hormuz."
OL,26,@tD@AOUvD@LO]vD@ZOUwD@gO]{D@AOU}D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
