OL,3,CTrump pauses operation to open Strait
OL,4,Cof Hormuz and pushes for Iran deal
OL,6,FSo far, only two merchant ships are
OL,7,Fknown to have passed through the new
OL,8,FUS-guarded route, with hundreds more
OL,9,Fbottled up in the Gulf.
OL,11,FSeparate to Project Freedom, Rubio
OL,12,Fsaid the major US military operation
OL,13,Fagainst Iran, dubbed "Operation Epic
OL,14,FFury", is over, but stopped short of
OL,15,Fsaying the conflict could not be
OL,16,Frestarted.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
