OL,3,CTrump pauses operation to open Strait
OL,4,Cof Hormuz and pushes for Iran deal
OL,6,FHe claimed this was because the
OL,7,Fobjectives of the mission were all
OL,8,Fsuccessfully concluded, adding: "We're
OL,9,Fnot cheering for an additional
OL,10,Fsituation to occur... We would prefer
OL,11,Fthe path of peace."
OL,13,FIn order for that to happen, Iran must
OL,14,Fagree to Trump's demands, but it is
OL,15,Funclear what the Islamic Republic's
OL,16,Fnext move will be.
OL,26,@pD@aOUsD@SO]
