OL,3,CTrump pauses operation to open Strait
OL,4,Cof Hormuz and pushes for Iran deal
OL,6,FThe announcement comes despite the UAE
OL,7,Freporting attacks by Iran on Tuesday
OL,8,Fevening, claiming it was "actively
OL,9,Fengaging" with missile and drone
OL,10,Fattack from Iran.
OL,12,FIran denied striking the UAE "in
OL,13,Frecent days," according to a statement
OL,14,Fby Ebrahim Zolfaghari, a spokesman for
OL,15,FIran's joint military command, that
OL,16,Fwas read Tuesday on state TV.
OL,18,FProposed UN resolution demands Iran
OL,19,Fhalt attacks on ships and stop
OL,20,F'illegal tolls'
OL,26,@pD@ZOUqD@IO]tD@^OUuD@MO]
