OL,3,CTrump pauses operation to open Strait
OL,4,Cof Hormuz and pushes for Iran deal
OL,6,FA proposed United Nations Security
OL,7,FCouncil resolution, co-sponsored by
OL,8,Fthe United States and Gulf nations,
OL,9,Fthreatens Iran with sanctions or other
OL,10,Fmeasures over its restriction of the
OL,11,FStrait of Hormuz.
OL,13,FIt calls on Tehran to restore freedom
OL,14,Fof navigation and immediately disclose
OL,15,Fwhere sea mines have been placed in
OL,16,Fand around the vital waterway, through
OL,17,Fwhich about a fifth of the world's oil
OL,18,Fand gas passes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
