PN,30513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778115794
OL,3,CTrump pauses operation to open Strait
OL,4,Cof Hormuz and pushes for Iran deal
OL,6,FThe draft, obtained on Tuesday by The
OL,7,FAssociated Press, also demands that
OL,8,FIran "immediately participate in and
OL,9,Fenable the United Nations efforts to
OL,10,Festablish a humanitarian corridor in
OL,11,Fthe strait" to enable vital aid,
OL,12,Ffertiliser and other goods to transit.
OL,14,FThe proposed resolution was drafted
OL,15,Funder Chapter 7 of the UN Charter,
OL,16,Fwhich can be enforced militarily.
OL,18,FIt threatens "effective measures that
OL,19,Fare commensurate with the gravity of
OL,20,Fthe situation, including sanctions" if
OL,21,FIran doesn't comply.
OL,26,@pD@FOUsD@KO]zD@NOU|D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
