OL,3,CTrump pauses operation to open Strait
OL,4,Cof Hormuz and pushes for Iran deal
OL,6,FA previous resolution aimed at opening
OL,7,Fthe Strait of Hormuz was vetoed by
OL,8,FRussia and China.
OL,10,FClashes continue between Hezbollah and
OL,11,FIsrael
OL,13,FIsrael's military said late on Tuesday
OL,14,Fthat Iran-backed Hezbollah militants
OL,15,Fin Lebanon had launched "several
OL,16,Frockets" toward Israeli soldiers in
OL,17,Fsouthern Lebanon.
OL,26,@wD@YOUxD@HO]
