OL,3,CTrump pauses operation to open Strait
OL,4,Cof Hormuz and pushes for Iran deal
OL,6,FNo injuries were reported. The Israel
OL,7,FDefence Forces (IDF) said it
OL,8,Fintercepted drones and what it calls
OL,9,F"aerial targets" launched by Hezbollah
OL,10,Fbefore they crossed into Israeli
OL,11,Fterritory.
OL,13,FHezbollah started firing at Israel a
OL,14,Ffew days after the beginning of the
OL,15,FIran war, which was triggered by a
OL,16,Fcampaign of airstrikes launched by
OL,17,FIsrael and the US on February 28.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@PO]
