OL,3,CTrump pauses operation to open Strait
OL,4,Cof Hormuz and pushes for Iran deal
OL,6,FIsrael responded with airstrikes and
OL,7,Flaunched a ground invasion of southern
OL,8,FLebanon. Hundreds of thousands of
OL,9,Fpeople have been displaced along the
OL,10,Fborder.
OL,12,FSince this latest round of conflict,
OL,13,F2,702 people in Lebanon have been
OL,14,Fkilled, according to the health
OL,15,Fministry in Beirut, while 8,311 have
OL,16,Fbeen injured during the same period.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
