OL,3,CTrump pauses operation to open Strait
OL,4,Cof Hormuz and pushes for Iran deal
OL,6,FA ceasefire between Israel and Lebanon
OL,7,Fhas been in place since April 17 but
OL,8,Fboth Israel and Hezbollah, which
OL,9,Foperated independently of the Beirut
OL,10,Fgovernment, have been carrying out
OL,11,Fdaily attacks since then.
